schema.notes: This dataset is designed for offline-first ventilator decision support. To capture any possible patient results, cases may include BOTH fixed common fields (clinicalParameters) and extensible observations/time series (observations, timeSeries).

observationModel.observations: Array of point-in-time results not covered by clinicalParameters (labs, imaging, ventilator measurements, medications, comorbidity scores, etc.).
observationModel.timeSeries: Array of timestamped values for trending (e.g., SpO2 over time, ventilator waveforms, urine output, MAP).

intendedUse.warning: Research/prototype dataset. Not clinically validated. Do not use as the sole basis for ventilator management decisions in real patients.
intendedUse.validationRequirement: For real-world use: populate from audited clinical sources, perform expert review, run retrospective/prospective validation, and comply with local ethics/regulatory requirements.
